config BR2_PACKAGE_GT_BE98_BR_BUSYBOX
	bool "gt-be98-br-busybox"
	help
	  Static busybox 1.37.0 for the /usr/br island. Built from the
	  hash-verified upstream tarball with the pinned config in this
	  package directory; harvested into the ASUS rootfs at
	  /usr/br/bin by board/gt-be98/rootfs-transform.sh (binary +
	  applet symlinks). Never installed to Buildroot's throwaway
	  target rootfs.
